			</td>
			<td>
			<p>Withhold enfortumab vedotin until elevated blood glucose has improved to &le;250 mg/dL, then resume treatment at the same dose level.</p>
			</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td rowspan="2">
			<p>Peripheral neuropathy</p>
			</td>
			<td>
			<p>Grade 2</p>
			</td>
			<td>
