	<li>CrCl &lt;15 mL minute: No data available; consider further dose reductions</li>
</ul>

<p><u><strong>Etoposide:</strong></u></p>

<p><strong>Hepatic:</strong>&nbsp;No dose adjustments in manufacturers labeling</p>

<p>Hendrayana, Wilmer, Kurth et al, 2017:</p>

