	<ul style="list-style-type:circle">
		<li><span style="font-family:Times">If toxicity worsens or does not improve, increase corticosteroid dose to prednisone 1 - 2 mg/kg/day (or equivalent).</span></li>
	</ul>
	</li>
	<li><span style="font-family:Times">Grade 4 creatinine elevation: Permanently discontinue; administer systemic corticosteroids (prednisone 1 - 2 mg/kg/day [or equivalent]) followed by a corticosteroid taper.</span></li>
</ul>

<p><strong><span style="font-family:Times">Hepatic Impairment</span></strong></p>

<p><em><span style="font-family:Times">Prior to treatment:</span></em></p>

