Yervoy (Ipilimumab) Medication Guide. U.S. Food and Drug Administration. https://www.accessdata.fda.gov/drugsatfda_docs/label/2015/125377s073lbl.pdf
', 'METASTATIC', '<p><strong>Ipilimumab</strong> 1 mg/kg IV on day 1<br />
