	<p><span style="font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif"><span class="marker"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="color:#232323">CrCl &ge;45 mL/minute: No dosage adjustment necessary. If Cr 45- 79 mL/minute with concomitant use of ibuprofen, avoid ibuprofen 2 days prior to treatment, day of treatment, and 2 days following.</span></span></span></span></p>
