<p><strong><span style="font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="color:#232323">Hepatic Impairment:</span></span></span></strong></p>

<ul>
	<li><span style="font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="color:#232323">No dosage instructions are provided in manufacturer&#39;s labeling</span></span></span></li>
