	If transaminase &lt; 10 upper normal limit and bilirubin 1.6-7.5 mg/dL, reduce to 50 mg/m2<br />
	If transaminase &gt; 10 upper normal limit or bilirubin &gt; 7.5 mg/dL, do not use</li>
